casebody.data:
PEOPLE
v.
VELA S242298 Supreme Court of California FEBRUARY 28, 2018 Votes: Cantil-Sakauye, C.J., Chin, Corrigan, Liu, Cuéllar and Kruger, JJ.

The above-entitled matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Fourth Appellate District, Division Three, with directions to vacate its decision and to reconsider the cause in light of SB 620 (Stats, 2017, ch. 682). ( Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(d).)
